<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">

  <title>Aventyr</title>

  <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/2.2.2/jquery.min.js"></script>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/materialize/0.100.2/css/materialize.min.css">
  <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/materialize/0.100.2/js/materialize.min.js"></script>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/style.css">
  <script src="./scripts/fontawesome-all.js"></script>
  <script src="./scripts/app.js"></script>

</head>
<body>
  <header class="center-align">
    <h1 class="center-align white-text">AveNtyr</h1>
    <img src="/images/aventyr.png" id = "main-page">
    </header>
  <nav class= "valign-wrapper grey lighten-1 sticky-nav-wrapper">
    <a href="/"><img src="/images/aventyr.png" id="logo"></a>
    <div>
      <a href="/api/cards">Gallery</a>
      <% if(!user) { %>
        <a href="" class="signup-btn">Sign up</a>
        <a href="/login" class="btn white black-text">Log In</a>
        <% } else { %>
          <a href="/api/users/<%=user.id%>"><%= user.username %></a>
          <a href="/logout" class="btn white black-text">Log Out</a>
          <% } %>
        </div>
      </nav>
      <main>
        <div class="row" id="sign-up">
        <form method="POST" action="/signup" class="col s4 offset-s4">
          <h3 class="center-align">Sign Up</h3>
          <div class="form-group">
            <input type="text" name="username" class="form-control" placeholder="Username" autofocus>
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <input type="text" name="email" class="form-control" placeholder="Email">
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <input type="password" name="password" class="form-control" placeholder="Password">
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <input type="submit" class="btn btn-block btn-primary" value="Sign Up">
          </div>
        </form>
      </div>
      <section class="row teal lighten-4">
        <div class="col s4 offset-s1">
          <h2>About us</h2>
          <p class="about">Love to travel? Looking for a new place to go? How about getting some inspiration? Checkout our Gallery to take inspiration from other traveller who've visited various destinations. Or you can create your own cards to give other motivation to travel more.</p>
        </div>
        <divclass="col s4 offset-s1">
          <img src="/images/header.jpg" class="about-image">
        </div>
      </section>

        <h3 class="center-align">Destinations</h3>
        <div class="container row carousel">
        <% for (let destination of destinations) { %>
          <div class="col s3 carousel-item">
            <img src="<%=destination.image%>">
            <h4 class="center-align"><%= destination.name %></h4>
          </div>
          <% } %>
        </div>
        <div class ="row light-blue lighten-4">
          <h4 class="center-align">Meet the Developers</h4>
          <div class="col s3 profile center-align"><img src="/images/omar2.jpg" class="profileimage"><p>Junior Full Stack Developer. Likes to stay active on the weekends either with sports or projects and staying up to date with the newest technology.
            Languages: HTML, CSS, Javascript, Ruby, Ruby on Rails, React, Node.js,Express
            Skills:Photoshop, Microsoft Word/Powerpoint, Photography
            Tools: Sublime, Atom, Github, Adobe Photoshop, Postman, Heroku, MongoDB</p>
          <a href="https://github.com/cubamex209" target="_blank" class="btn github">Github</a></div>
          <div class="col s3 profile center-align"><img src="https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/C5603AQFH2j__1g97qw/profile-displayphoto-shrink_800_800/0?e=1526688000&v=alpha&t=5tQc96-0LJZ7hMFzizaHtUszaA9cjVqpxnw1WZqFZCY" class="profileimage"><p>Web Development student in the San Francisco Bay Area learning new technologies and build on different skills. Would love to collaborate on new projects.
            Skills: HTML, CSS, JavaScript, jQuery, AJAX/JSON,Ruby, Node.js, Angular, Ruby on Rails, React, API integration, OOP, mySQL, Bootstrap, MongoDB, Express.js
            Github: https://github.com/Manjilan
            Website: http://manjilanakarmi.com</p>
            <a href="https://github.com/Manjilan" target="_blank" class="btn github">Github</a></div>
          <div class="col s3 profile center-align"><img src="https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/C5603AQFljn9hFHfBQQ/profile-displayphoto-shrink_800_800/0?e=1526688000&v=alpha&t=kw1VNqZqwmYO7zGk0a_nayrwYa2Koqu0P5dVZf0XnZw" class="profileimage"><p>The tech industry has transformative powers and as a developer, my aim is to utilize these to solve business challenges and build beautiful and meaningful things.
            Skills: Javascript, AJAX, JQuery, Node.js/Express, Ruby, Ruby on Rails, PostgreSQL, MsSQL, MongoDB, React, HTML5, CSS3 </p>
          <a href="https://github.com/spotthebug" target="_blank" class="btn github">Github</a></div>
          </div>

      </main>
      <section class="row info card-panel">
        <div class="col s1 offset-s2">
          <p>Facebook</p>
          <p>Instagram</p>
          <p>LinkedIn</p>
          <p>E-mail Us</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col s1 offset-s1">
          <p>Terms </p>
          <p>Privacy Policy</p>
          <p>Travel</p>
          <p>Business</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col s1 offset-s1">
          <p>Press</p>
          <p>Policies</p>
          <p>Social Responsiblity</p>
          <p>Help</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col s1 offset-s1">
          <p>Careers</p>
          <p>Volunteering</p>
          <p>Contact Us</p>
          <p>FAQs</p>
        </div>
      </section>
      <footer>
        <p class="center-align grey">Â© Aventyr</p>
      </footer>
    </body>
    </html>
